T02TD1226E:29b-1: shr'i ae ka p'i ra s'a dha nam n'a ma /
T02TD1226E:29b-3: dpal dpa' bo gcig pa zhes bya ba'i sgrub pa'i thabs /
T02TD1226E:29b-4: kye rdo rje la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1226E:29b-5: snying rje shes rab gnyis med bdag / he ru ka dang bdag med dang //
T02TD1226E:29b-6: rdo rje slob dpon zhabs padma //
T02TD1226E:29b-7: phyag 'tshal dpa' bo gcig pa bri //
T02TD1226E:29b-8: bya mang rgan po blo dman pas //
T02TD1226E:29b-9: dngos grub thob phyir rab tu bsdus //
T02TD1226E:30a-2: rdo rje slob dpon yang dag pa la kye rdo rje las gsungs pa'i rim pas sems legs par sbyangs pas ji skad gsungs pa'i gsung nyams dga' bar legs par sbyangs pa'i shes rab dang /
T02TD1226E:30a-3: 'dod pa'i longs spyod kyis bde bar gnas par bya'o //
T02TD1226E:30a-4: de nas phyi nang gi khrus dang mchod pa dang gtor ma tshogs pa dang /
T02TD1226E:30a-5: rang gi snying gar nyi ma la h'um dkar po 'od zer lnga dang ldan pa'i 'od kyi snang bas nam mkha' la bla ma dang sangs rgyas yang dag par gsal ba la //
T02TD1226E:30a-6: lha mo brgyad kyi phyag na bdud rtsi lnga dang /
T02TD1226E:30a-10: de'i mdun na sdig pa bshags pa dang /
T02TD1226E:30a-12: rjes su yi rang ba dang /
T02TD1226E:30a-14: dkon mchog gsum la skyabs su 'gro ba dang //
T02TD1226E:30a-16: tshangs pa'i gnas bzhi bsgom par bya'o //
T02TD1226E:30a-17: de nas snod bcud thams cad snying ga'i 'od zer gyis bsregs la /
T02TD1226E:30a-18: aom sh'u n+ya t'a dzny'a na badzra sva bh'a ba a'atma ko& ham /
T02TD1226E:30a-19: zhes brjod pas mi dmigs par bsgom /
T02TD1226E:30a-20: de nas sngon gyi smon lam gyi stobs kyis nam mkha' la padma dang nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor gyi dbus su h'um yongs su gyur pa las sna tshogs rdo rjer gyur /
T02TD1226E:30a-22: 'dus pa las rdo rje'i ra ba dang /
T02TD1226E:30a-24: sa gzhi la sogs pa rgyas par bsgom /
T02TD1226E:30a-25: de'i dbus su shes rab ae'i dbyibs 'dra ba bsgom mo //
T02TD1226E:30a-37: bdag nyid gcig tu gyur pa las /
T02TD1226E:30a-38: gzhal yas khang gru bzhi rta babs bzhi pa /
T02TD1226E:30a-41: nyi zla dang sna tshogs pa'i dar dang /
T02TD1226E:30a-42: me tog la sogs pa 'dod pa'i yon tan lngas brgyan pa dur khrod brgyad kyi dbus su bsgom mo //
T02TD1226E:30a-43: de'i dbus su padma dmar po dang /
T02TD1226E:30a-44: nyi ma'i dbus su tshangs pa dang dbang po dang khyab 'jug dang /
T02TD1226E:30a-45: drag po'i snying khar dbyangs dang gsal byed gnyis yongs su gyur pa las /
T02TD1226E:30a-47: de'i dbus su aam dang h'u% las gri gug dang thod pa /
T02TD1226E:30b-0: aam h'u% gis mtshan pa spro ba dang bsdu ba'i mtshan nyid can @30b bsam mo //
T02TD1226E:30b-1: thams cad gcig tu gyur pa las //
T02TD1226E:30b-2: bdag nyid dpal kye rdo rje bdag med ma dang bde ba sdom pa /
T02TD1226E:30b-4: phyag bcu drug pa zhabs bzhi pa /
T02TD1226E:30b-5: sku mdog zla ba dang shel lta bu dang /
T02TD1226E:30b-6: rtsa ba'i zhal sku lta bu /
T02TD1226E:30b-8: g-yon dmar po gzhan ni bung ba ltar gtsigs pa /
T02TD1226E:30b-9: phyag g-yas pa'i thod pa brgyad na /
T02TD1226E:30b-18: de bzhin du g-yon pa brgyad na /
T02TD1226E:30b-30: stag lpags kyi sham thabs dang /
T02TD1226E:30b-33: skra ser po gyen du 'bar ba la /
T02TD1226E:30b-34: sna tshogs rdo rjes mtshan pa /
T02TD1226E:30b-35: spyan nyi shu rtsa bzhis phyug pa /
T02TD1226E:30b-36: phyed krung bcas pas bdud kyi steng na rol pa /
T02TD1226E:30b-37: bdag med ma nag mo zhal gcig phyag gnyis ma /
T02TD1226E:30b-38: skra ser po gyen du 'bar ba /
T02TD1226E:30b-44: stag lpags kyi sham thabs can /
T02TD1226E:30b-45: gri gug dang thod pa 'dzin pa'i phyag gis gtso bo'i mgul nas 'khyud pa /
T02TD1226E:30b-46: gnyis su med pa'i man ngag gis gnas par bya'o //
T02TD1226E:30b-47: de nas snying ga'i sa bon las 'od zer lcags kyu'i gzugs kyis ye shes sems dpa' spyan drangs la /
T02TD1226E:30b-50: gnyis su med par bstim par bya'o //
T02TD1226E:30b-58: gti mug rdo rje la sogs pa /
T02TD1226E:30b-67: kha tv'am ga bsnams par bsgom par bya'o //
T02TD1226E:30b-68: de nas thugs ka'i 'od zer gyi lcags kyus de bzhin gshegs pa spyan drangs la mchod pa bya ste /
T02TD1226E:30b-69: aa bhi shinytsa tu m'am sarba ta th'a ga ta zhes gsol ba btab pas /
T02TD1226E:30b-70: de dag he ru ka'i gzugs su gyur pas /
T02TD1226E:30b-71: bdud rtsi'i bum pas dbang bskur bas /
T02TD1226E:30b-72: rigs kyi bdag pos spyi bor mtshan par bsam mo //
T02TD1226E:31a-1: rnal 'byor bla ma'i man ngag gis bsgoms pas /
T02TD1226E:31a-2: brtags pa'i mtshan ma la sogs pa'i rim pas dngos grub thob po //
T02TD1226E:31a-3: bskyed pa'i rim pa dga' ba yis //
T02TD1226E:31a-4: rtsa sogs gsang sngags btu bzlas nas //
T02TD1226E:31a-5: 'byung po che la gtor ma byin //
T02TD1226E:31a-6: dkyil 'khor la sogs las rnams bya /
T02TD1226E:31a-7: goo r'i glu blang 'dod longs spyod //
T02TD1226E:31a-8: dka' thub mi spyad bde bas bsgrub //
T02TD1226E:31a-9: bdud rtsi lnga po rtag tu bza' //
T02TD1226E:31a-10: zhal brgyad rnam par thar pa brgyad //
T02TD1226E:31a-11: bcu drug phyag ni stong pa ste //
T02TD1226E:31a-12: zhabs bzhi bsdu ba'i dngos po bzhi //
T02TD1226E:31a-13: spyan gsum po ni sku gsum yin //
T02TD1226E:31a-14: snying rje'i spyan ni dmar po ste //
T02TD1226E:31a-15: yan lag nag po byams pa'i sems //
T02TD1226E:31a-16: gug skyed rnam dag sangs rgyas lnga //
T02TD1226E:31a-17: khro bo gdug pa 'dul ba po //
T02TD1226E:31a-18: phung po lnga ni mdor bsdu na //
T02TD1226E:31a-19: rdo rje ma sogs lha mo lnga //
T02TD1226E:31a-20: khams bzhi dag pas lha mo bzhi //
T02TD1226E:31a-21: mig sogs gti mug rdo rje sogs //
T02TD1226E:31a-22: yul sogs dag pa lha mo drug / yang dag par ni rang bzhin med //
T02TD1226E:31a-23: dag pas dug med byas nas ni //
T02TD1226E:31a-24: bsten bya 'di dag bsten par bya //
T02TD1226E:31a-25: spyod lam dag ni ci spyad dang //
T02TD1226E:31a-26: rtag tu de nyid dran byas na //
T02TD1226E:31a-28: shes rab rgyud kyi snying po kye yi rdo rje rgya mtsho las //
T02TD1226E:31a-29: de nyid bsdus pa dpa' bo gcig pa'i sgrub pa'i thabs //
T02TD1226E:31a-30: gsal bar byas pa'i dge ba gang yin des //
T02TD1226E:31a-31: 'gro ba ma lus dngos grub thob par shog / dpal dpa' bo gcig pa zhes bya ba'i sgrub pa'i thabs //
T02TD1226E:31a-32: slob dpon rdo rje dril bus mdzad pa rdzogs so /
T02TD1226E:31a-34: // / rgya gar gyi mkhan po ga ya dha ra dang /
T02TD1226E:31a-35: dge slong sh'akya ye shes kyis bsgyur cing gtan la phab ba'o //
